flowchart TD
    A([User input]) --> B[Rule-based filter: blocked keywords and jailbreak patterns]
    B --> C{Rule violation?}
    C -- Yes --> D([Return policy refusal])
    C -- No --> E[Moderation classifier: score harm categories]
    E --> F{Score above threshold?}
    F -- Yes --> D
    F -- No --> G[PII detection: scan for emails, phone numbers, SSNs]
    G --> H{PII found?}
    H -- Block --> D
    H -- Redact --> I[Redact PII from input]
    H -- Clean --> J[Forward sanitized input to LLM]
    I --> J
    J --> K[LLM generates draft response]
    K --> L[Output moderation classifier]
    L --> M{Output flagged?}
    M -- Yes --> N{Severity level?}
    N -- High --> O([Return fallback refusal response])
    N -- Low --> P([Escalate to human review queue])
    M -- No --> Q{Grounding check required?}
    Q -- Yes --> R[Verify citations against retrieved sources]
    R --> S{Grounded?}
    S -- No --> T([Return grounding warning with response])
    S -- Yes --> U([Return response to user])
    Q -- No --> U
